  79,39,the Hellfire will certainly be ňĻtheirňļ home
  79,40,And as for those who were in awe of standing before their Lord and restrained themselves from ňĻevilňļ desires
  79,41,Paradise will certainly be ňĻtheirňļ home
  79,42,"They ask you ňĻO Prophetňļ regarding the Hour, ‚ÄúWhen will it be?‚ÄĚ"
  79,43,But it is not for you to tell its time
